        <briefdescription>
<para>Computes Hankel transform, using digital filters. </para>
        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para><simplesect kind="note"><para>Corresponds to strategies 6-11 in SASfit. </para>
</simplesect>
<simplesect kind="note"><para>Does not allow any error control. </para>
</simplesect>
<simplesect kind="note"><para>Perform wells for simple form factors, but it does struggle with oscillatory ones. For oscillatory form factors, it is advisable to start with this method for a rough Hankel transform computation, and then refine it with &quot;hankel_transform_QWE_Chave&quot; or &quot;hankel_transform_QWE_Key&quot;.</para>
</simplesect>
<parameterlist kind="param"><parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>nu</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>order of bessel function - must be 0 or 1 </para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
<parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>f</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>pointer to function to transform </para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
<parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>x</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>value at which to compute the transform </para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
<parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>f_ctx</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>pointer to struct containing inputs for f </para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
<parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>output</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>pointer to var containing output from transform </para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
<parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>n_strategy</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>an integer number between 6 and 11 (determines which weightings to use for the transform and corresponds to SASfit strategies 6-11) </para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
</parameterlist>
</para>
